SRK: Censor Board’s Recent List is not a Finalized List; It’s Probably Just the Guidelines!

Many of the famous Bollywood Filmmakers like Hansal Mehta and Anurag Kashayp and many others had done many complaints regarding the unjustified ban of Censor Board for using cuss words in the films. The King of romance also got tricked during an event few days back, and what Shah Rukh Khan said regarding this was correct.


